# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  selah-mpk-mini-iv — MPK mini IV Preset Editor
#  Part of SelahBridgePro — Selah Technologies LLC — Copyright (C) 2026
#
#  Native replacement for the Windows Akai MPK mini IV editor.
#  Protocol confirmed from live hardware (USB VID:09e8 PID:005d).
#
#  Usage:
#    selah-mpk-mini-iv              launch GUI editor
#    selah-mpk-mini-iv --ports      list MIDI ports and exit
#    selah-mpk-mini-iv --monitor    print raw MIDI messages
